T1  - Throttling hyperactive robots – Order-to-trade ratios at the Oslo Stock Exchange
AU  - Jørgensen, Kjell
AU  - Skjeltorp, Johannes
AU  - Ødegaard, Bernt Arne
JO  - Journal of Financial Markets
VL  - 37
SP  - 1
EP  - 16
