T1  - Evolution of historical prices in momentum investing
AU  - Chen, Li-Wen
AU  - Yu, Hsin-Yi
AU  - Wang, Wen-Kai
JO  - Journal of Financial Markets
VL  - 37
SP  - 120
EP  - 135
